---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ChatConversation from '../../components/ChatConversation.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Whiteboard Analysis | Live Knowledge" description="Turn brainstorming sessions into structured notes and action items">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 via-slate-50 to-blue-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Whiteboard Analysis
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Transform brainstorming sessions, meeting notes, and whiteboard sketches into 
          structured action plans, organized insights, and clear next steps.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Case Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Scenario -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Scenario</h2>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-orange-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-orange-900 mb-4">Product Strategy Meeting</h3>
            <p class="text-orange-800 mb-6">
              After a 2-hour brainstorming session, your team's whiteboard is covered with ideas, 
              user personas, feature concepts, and scattered action items. Rather than spending 
              another hour trying to make sense of the handwritten chaos, you take a photo.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-orange-200">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900">What's on the whiteboard:</span>
              </div>
              <ul class="text-slate-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>• User personas sketched in different corners</li>
                <li>• Feature ideas with pros/cons lists</li>
                <li>• Timeline with key milestones</li>
                <li>• Action items assigned to different team members</li>
                <li>• Risk factors circled in red</li>
                <li>• Revenue projections in a rough table</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pattern In Action -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Pattern in Action</h2>
          <ChatConversation 
            messages={[
              {
                type: 'user',
                content: 'I\'m attaching a photo of our product strategy whiteboard from today\'s brainstorming session. Can you help me organize this into a structured summary with clear action items?',
                hasAttachment: true,
                attachmentType: 'image'
              },
              {
                type: 'assistant', 
                content: `# Product Strategy Session Summary

## Key User Personas Identified
1. **Tech-Savvy Early Adopter** (Sarah, 28)
   - Values: Innovation, efficiency, cutting-edge features
   - Pain points: Current tools too basic

2. **Busy Professional** (Mike, 45) 
   - Values: Reliability, ease of use, time-saving
   - Pain points: Complex interfaces, steep learning curve

3. **Budget-Conscious Startup** (Team leads)
   - Values: Cost-effectiveness, scalability
   - Pain points: Expensive enterprise solutions

## Prioritized Feature Roadmap
**Phase 1 (Q1):**
- Core dashboard functionality
- Basic reporting features
- Mobile responsiveness

**Phase 2 (Q2):** 
- Advanced analytics
- Third-party integrations
- Collaboration tools

**Phase 3 (Q3):**
- AI-powered insights
- Custom workflows
- Enterprise features

## Action Items by Owner
**Sarah (Product):**
- [ ] Create detailed user research plan (Due: Next Friday)
- [ ] Validate persona assumptions with 10 customer interviews

**Mike (Engineering):**
- [ ] Technical feasibility assessment for Phase 1 features
- [ ] Architecture design document (Due: 2 weeks)

**Jessica (Design):**
- [ ] Wireframes for core dashboard (Due: 10 days)
- [ ] User journey mapping for each persona

**David (Marketing):**
- [ ] Competitive analysis deep-dive 
- [ ] Go-to-market strategy for early adopters

## Risk Factors to Monitor
⚠️ **High Priority:**
- Competitor X launching similar feature in Q2
- Limited engineering bandwidth for Q1 timeline

⚠️ **Medium Priority:** 
- User research may invalidate core assumptions
- Integration complexity higher than estimated

## Revenue Projections
- Q1: $50K ARR (100 customers @ $500/year)
- Q2: $200K ARR (400 customers)
- Q3: $500K ARR (1000 customers)

*Next meeting: Review user research findings and finalize Q1 scope*`
              }
            ]}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Benefits -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">Why This Works</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Instant Organization</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            No more spending meeting time transcribing messy notes. Get structured output immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Actionable Output</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Transform scattered ideas into clear action items with owners and deadlines.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Team Alignment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Everyone leaves with the same understanding and clear next steps.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pro Tips -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">Pro Tips</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Take Multiple Angles</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Capture photos from different angles if text is hard to read or if there are overlapping elements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Provide Context</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Include meeting purpose, attendees, and any specific organizational preferences in your prompt.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Specify Output Format</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Ask for specific formats: "organize as a project brief," "create a task list," or "format as meeting minutes."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>